query:
SELECT
                number,
                timestamp,
                protocol_version,
                fee_address,
                l1_gas_price,
                l2_fair_gas_price,
                fair_pubdata_price,
                pubdata_limit,
                settlement_layer_type,
                settlement_layer_chain_id
            FROM (
                SELECT
                    number,
                    timestamp,
                    protocol_version,
                    fee_address,
                    l1_gas_price,
                    l2_fair_gas_price,
                    fair_pubdata_price,
                    pubdata_limit,
                    is_sealed,
                    settlement_layer_type,
                    settlement_layer_chain_id
                FROM l1_batches
                ORDER BY number DESC
                LIMIT 1
            ) AS u
            WHERE NOT is_sealed
